name: Experiment Or Die #91
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. This piece is about needing and having to go with the natural flow of things despite at times needing to reset yourself. I've been trying to get back to the original roots of the collection with more open space but have found it hard to dial back the color. I want to go where each piece takes me but am actively trying to steer the balloon into some more minimal waters. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
